=head1 NAME

list-regexp-pattern-patterns - List Regexp::Pattern::* patterns

=head1 VERSION

This document describes version 0.004 of list-regexp-pattern-patterns (from Perl distribution App-RegexpPatternUtils), released on 2020-01-03.

=head1 SYNOPSIS

